Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 3

This is a python library for sending email messages which is part of the Python standard library. 
The original email package does not give you the flexibility as this one. 
This library gives you the flexibility to send emails with attachments, HTML content and email subject. 
It also supports sending emails with multiple recipients and single attachments.
This package is compatible with Python 3 and later versions.

